{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2015}} {{Infobox person | image = | image_size = | name = Johann Graf | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{bya|1946}} | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | restingplace = | nationality = Austrian | religion = | ethnicity = | residence = [[Vienna]], Austria | education = | alma mater = | occupation = Owner, [[Novomatic]] | salary = | networth = [[United States dollar|$]]8.1 billion (March 2018)<ref name=Forbes>{{cite web|title=Johann Graf|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/johann-graf/|website=Forbes|accessdate=4 November 2018}}</ref> | spouse = | parents = | children = 3 | relatives = | website = }}
'''Johann Graf''' (born 1946) is an Austrian businessman, the founder and owner of [[Novomatic]], an Austrian gambling company.
==Early life== Graf was born in Austria in 1946.<ref name=Forbes/> Graf was born in a one bedroom flat and was raised by his grandparents. His first line of work was an apprentice butcher and it was presumed that he would follow in the line of the family business and assume control of the family’s butcher shop. It was in 1974 when he decided that he would venture off on his own. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://fastlifeluxury.com/johann-graf/|title=JOHANN GRAF|publisher=Fast Life Luxury|date=July 8, 2015}}</ref>
==Career== Graf’s professional career started in 1974. It was then that Graf and Gerhard Brodnik founded Brodnik & Graf GmbH. This company specialized in importing Belgian pinball machines to be set up in pubs, cafes and brothels.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.therichest.com/celebnetworth/celebrity-business/men/johann-graf-net-worth/|title=Johann Graf Net Worth|publisher=The Richest|date=July 8, 2015}}</ref>
==Personal life== Graf is divorced with three children and lives in Vienna. He collects vintage cars and owns some 120, most of which are [[Jaguar Cars|Jaguar]]s.<ref name=Forbes/> The eldest of his three children is the chief technology officer of [[Novomatic]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.therichest.com/celebnetworth/celebrity-business/men/johann-graf-net-worth/|title=JOHANN GRAF|publisher=Fast Life Luxury|date=July 8, 2015}} </ref>
According to ''[[Forbes]]''’ list of global billionaires, he is listed at number 208 with a net worth of $7 billion as of July 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/johann-graf/?list=billionaires|title=#208 Johann Graf|publisher=Forbes|date=July 8, 2015}}</ref>
